snippet.title: Amber Heard LOVES nerds! Desperate to win over comic fans!
snippet.description:
While Johnny Depp is having a hard time, Heard is doing just fine! Working with royalty, getting paid thousands for public speaking, and now shooting scene for The Snyder Cut! Word is Warner wants her to be as big as Wonder Woman! But can she win over comic fans? She thinks so!
